Summary[edit]

English: The flag of Antigua and Barbuda
Afrikaans: Vlag van Antigua en Barbuda
Bosanski: Zastava Antigve i Barbude
Deutsch: Die Flagge von Antigua und Barbuda.
ދިވެހިބަސް: ދިދަ އެންޓިގުއާ އަދި ބާބިއުޑާ
Ελληνικά: Σημαία των Αντίγκουα και Μπαρμπούντα
فارسی: پرچم آنتیگوا و باربودا
Suomi: Antiguan ja Barbudan lippu
Français : Le drapeau d'Antigua-et-Barbuda
हिन्दी: एन्टिगुवा और बारबूडा का ध्वज
Magyar: Antigua és Barbuda zászlaja.
한국어: 한국어 설명:이 국기는 앤티가바부다 국기입니다.
Nederlands: Vlag van Antigua en Barbuda
Português: A bandeira de Antígua e Barbuda
Русский: Флаг Антигуа и Барбуды
Kiswahili: Bendera ya Antigua na Barbuda
Türkçe: Antigua ve Barbuda Bayrağı
اردو: اینٹیگوا و باربوڈا کا پرچم

David Benbennick wrote this file, based on the information at Flags of the World. The colors are those given at Vexilla Mundi: rgb(206,17,38) for red, rgb(0,114,198) for blue, and rgb(252,209,22) for yellow.

The Flag Creator: The flag dates from the achievement of self-government in 1967. It was the winning design in a competition that more than 600 local people entered. The designer and winner was Sir Reginald Samuel.
